Third-party dependencies (installed separately, NOT redistributed here)
------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository does not bundle third-party code. The tools below are
installed by the user during setup (see README, "Local setup"); each is
governed solely by its own license, not by this project's Apache-2.0 license.

1. PlantUML (plantuml.jar)
   Installed to: wiki/.obsidian/plantuml/plantuml.jar (gitignored)
   License: GNU GPL v3 (the GPL distribution of PlantUML)
   Source: https://plantuml.com / https://github.com/plantuml/plantuml

2. obsidian-plantuml (Obsidian community plugin)
   Installed via Obsidian's community plugin browser
   License: per the plugin's own repository
   Source: https://github.com/joethei/obsidian-plantuml

3. Smart Connections (Obsidian community plugin)
   Installed via Obsidian's community plugin browser
   License: per the plugin's own repository
   Source: https://github.com/brianpetro/obsidian-smart-connections

4. Obsidian Agent Skills (obsidian-markdown, obsidian-bases, obsidian-cli,
   json-canvas, defuddle)
   Installed by setup.sh / setup.ps1 into .claude/skills/ (gitignored)
   License: MIT
   Source: https://github.com/kepano/obsidian-skills

The repository commits only its own small Obsidian config (which plugins to
enable, and the PlantUML SVG/local-JAR settings) and its OWN Claude Code skills
(init-wiki, voice-interview, deep-recon) and the pr-manager agent, so the right
configuration applies once the third-party tools above are installed.
